<div id="pf38b4" class="pf w55 h237" data-page-no="38b4"><div class="pc pc38b4 w55 h237"><div class="t m645 xd2 h4e y2b06 ff3 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 9 </div><div class="t m308 x57 h35 y2a77 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">February 25 to March 3 </div><div class="t m64c xb7 h104 y1229 ff3 fs1c fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">BARRIERS TO EFFECTIVE COMMUNICATION </div><div class="t m808 xda h5 y12e5 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;The Lord&apos;s arm is not so short that </div><div class="t m2d5 xd0 h5 y862 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">he cannot save nor his ear too dull to </div><div class="t m18e1 xd0 h5 yaba ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hear; it is your iniquities that raise a bar-</div><div class="t m67c xd0 h5 y770 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rier between you and your God, because </div><div class="t m9a1 xd0 h5 yaf4 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of your sins he has hidden his face so </div><div class="t mcd3 xd0 h5 y79b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that he does not hear you.&quot; Isa. 59:1, 2, </div><div class="t m4f xd0 h5 y40c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NEB. </div><div class="t mab1 x0 h35 y1205 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;It is the privilege of every soul to be </div><div class="t m27e xd1 h35 y4b6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a living channel through which God can </div><div class="t m555 xd1 h35 y73 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">communicate to the world the treasures </div><div class="t m6e7 xd1 h35 y15ac ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of His grace, the unsearchable riches of </div><div class="t m29e xd1 h35 y4b7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ. There is nothing that Christ desires </div><div class="t m3f xd1 h35 y1aa ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">so much as agents who will represent to </div><div class="t mb1b xd1 h35 yf82 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the world His Spirit and character. There </div><div class="t m109 xd1 h35 y8f2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is nothing that the world needs so much </div><div class="t m32a xd1 h35 y126e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as the manifestation through humanity of </div><div class="t m295 xd1 h35 y3f6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Saviour&apos;s love. All heaven is waiting </div><div class="t m40b xd1 h35 yaff ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for channels through which can be poured </div><div class="t m85d xd1 h35 y814 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the holy oil to be a joy and blessing to </div><div class="t m9ff xd1 h35 y481 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">human hearts.&quot;â€”Christ&apos;s </div><div class="t m559 x51 h35 y533 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Object Lessons, </div><div class="t m57d xd1 h35 yab3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">page 419. </div><div class="t m2bb x0 h35 y14be ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Problems within us sometimes prevent </div><div class="t m5e2 xd1 h35 y3b7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">effective communications. The originator </div><div class="t m3bb xd1 h35 y150f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the message does not give a clear  </div><div class="t m649 x7a h35 y3a7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">signal. Frequently the message itself is </div><div class="t m9f5 x7a h35 y473 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">distorted. We do not state it accurately </div><div class="t m88f x7a h35 y17 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and cleanly. Then the signal may be </div><div class="t me81 x7a h35 y1c2b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">blurred as it comes to the receiver. </div><div class="t me94 x8f h35 ya7a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What obstacles wait in the minds and </div><div class="t m26c x7a h35 y513 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hearts of those to whom we seek to com-</div><div class="t m9c1 x7a h35 y705 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">municate the gospel? The false informa-</div><div class="t m398 x7a h35 y9f6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tion about God and the ideal human life </div><div class="t m288 x7a h35 y1205 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">which Satan has propagated is an obsta-</div><div class="t ma4 x7a h35 y4b6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cle in many minds to the communication </div><div class="t m313 x7a h35 y73 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the truth. Satan gave the first deceptive </div><div class="t m16d x7a h35 y15ac ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">signal, and he continues this confusing </div><div class="t m14a x7a h35 y3c1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">work. The story of the great controversy </div><div class="t m811 x7a h35 y1015 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">between Christ and Satan is the story of </div><div class="t m1584 x7a h35 yf82 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the establishment of truth in face of the </div><div class="t m7e7 x7a h35 y8f2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">opposition of error. What are the barriers </div><div class="t m318 x52 h35 y7c1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that hold back the flow of divine communi-</div><div class="t md8 x52 h35 yf54 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cation through us to the needy world? </div><div class="t m615 x90 h35 y51c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This is not specifically a lesson about </div><div class="t ma7c x7a h35 y814 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prayer communication with God, but in </div><div class="t m990 x52 h35 y871 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">considering the barriers raised between </div><div class="t m906 x52 h35 y914 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God and man and between man and man </div><div class="t mf32 x52 h35 y14be ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">we find ourselves closely involved with the </div><div class="t m9d2 x52 h35 y2f6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reasons for or against successful com-</div><div class="t m3f5 x52 h35 y150f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">munication between God and man. </div><div class="t m522 x195 h35 y23cf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">67 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
